hật ngộ vũ - 初九日遇雨</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Du/author-_WwJUp8k9thJYDiKeky3PA">Phạm Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-Th%C3%A2n/S%C6%A1-s%C6%A1n/poem-L4D2_8QzLSaKHC8MMZJJxA">Sơ sơn - 疏山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%E1%BA%A3i-Th%C3%A2n/author-DQf8qNg6lJ8c_3ivuKiNlw">Ngải Thân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/T%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-tPpPVGWZUtiiAX5gPlMJCQ">Tức sự - 即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-05/poem-4sXqerHyEUlcQEzOcEHDVg">Xuân nhật tuyệt cú thập thủ kỳ 05 - 春日絕句十首其五</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br></div>	</div>
